334	            lineHeight: 1.7,
335	            maxWidth: "34rem",
336	          }}
337	        >
338	          <div>market → corpus → metrics → rule graph → decision → safety → ledger</div>
339	          <div>paper: PaperBetEngine | live: safety.check_all_gates → LiveBetEngine</div>
340	        </div>
